results.deck: Conspiracy Entertainment is a publisher of games that helps out small development studios by helping them publish their games when they are having a tough time doing so. Founded in 1997 (originally as Conspiracy Games), Conspiracy Entertainment has gone on to become a recognized publisher of smaller titles.
